beer.beer_description: Acid on the sleeve. Ether in the trunk. Lawyer in the bath. Reptiles at the zoo. Poolside at the Flamingo. Excess while entertaining, seldom goes well. So when creating this lager, we layered in Sorachi Ace hops for a fruity hit and made sure to add just the right amount of rice, drying it out while giving it a more muscular alcohol kick. This is rice country, after all.
